This upgrade allows the use of color codes.  The same color 
codes used for xtitle ([1;37m help xtitle[2;37;0m and [1;37mhinfo color[2;37;0m) can be used for 
setting item, short, and long descriptions.  This upgrade comes with 
palaces automatically. 

[1;30mSee also: color, upgrades, upgrades list
